                            <comment id="17337981" author="paulk" created="Sun, 2 May 2021 09:13:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Possible duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-7252&quot; title=&quot;Integer literal not accepted for primitive short annotation attribute&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-7252&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-7252&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17562807" author="emilles" created="Tue, 5 Jul 2022 18:45:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;org.apache.groovy.ast.tools.ExpressionUtils.transformInlineConstants(Expression)&lt;/tt&gt; does not transfer the target type.  So &quot;TestCode.SHORT_1&quot; becomes &quot;ConstantExpression(1, int)&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
